transferpy (1.0) buster-wikimedia; urgency=medium

  * Add automatic port detection.
  * Add fast parallel-checksum option for network related integrity checks.
  * Make source checksum parallel to data transfer.
  * Resolve all the concurrency issues.
  * Add more tests and documentation.
  * Enable configuration file for user arguments.

